One. two. three. four.
five. six. seven. eight.

35
00:02:36.430 --> 00:02:38.810
Ah.

36
00:02:48.270 --> 00:02:51.720
Twenty-eight. 29. 30.
Okay. this way. It's fine.

37
00:02:52.640 --> 00:02:54.270
Thirty-one. 32. 33.

38
