116
00:07:34.930 --> 00:07:37.180
Oh. really? All this time. I had no idea.

117
00:07:37.270 --> 00:07:39.116
- When a horse gets pregnant...
- God. the horse.

118
00:07:39.140 --> 00:07:42.970
You know about horses? When a horse
