126
00:07:58.520 --> 00:08:00.930
Hold on.
Our father was off on a faraway stud farm.

127
00:08:01.020 --> 00:08:03.560
- That is correct.
- That is correct.

128
00:08:04.600 --> 00:08:05.770
Poor us.

129
00:08:05.850 --> 00:08:09.390
We should go feel sorry for ourselves
