- Code gray. Level one.

163
00:10:06.430 --> 00:10:08.270
Calm down. Security!

164
00:10:18.350 --> 00:10:20.770
- You feel better?
- It's happening now.

165
00:10:20.850 --> 00:10:21.720
You get any on you?

166
00:10:21.810 --> 00:10:24.390
The thing in Russia that's making
