he was walking his kids to school.

843
01:03:33.600 --> 01:03:36.180
In the middle of all that shit.

844
01:03:36.770 --> 01:03:39.270
all that chaos.
he was walking his kids to school.

845
01:03:46.350 --> 01:03:47.350
So...

846
